query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('13.04',
'google-chrome',
'installation',
'login',
'mouse',
'multiple-monitors',
'nautilus',
'permissions',
'python',
'updates',
'usb',
'virtualbox',
'xubuntu');
